data.title: Naughty by Nature: Written on Ya Kitten (Music Video 1993)
data.meta_description: Naughty by Nature: Written on Ya Kitten: Directed by Anthony 'Treach' Criss, Richard Lewis. With Naughty By Nature, Anthony 'Treach' Criss, DJ Kay Gee, Pepa. Naughty by Nature performs in the music video "Written on Ya Kitten" from the album "19 Naughty III" recorded for Tommy Boy Records. The video begins shots of a kittens in an apartment. Naughty by Nature raps on the fire escape, at a pool, and at a variety of other locations. Clips of women and kittens play throughout.
